<div class="com-share" data-id="6906" data-title="《《平凡的世界》开播，你曾经期待过它吗？》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/6906/medium/6906.jpg?1436697569" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/6906.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
